an arm and a leg in the process.
Why? For the skins.

445
00:31:20,530 --> 00:31:22,706
We're no longer cavemen.

446
00:31:22,750 --> 00:31:27,407
You're absolutely right.
Times change, fashions change,
animal skins are no longer in.

447
00:31:27,450 --> 00:31:29,409
But the concept
remains the same.

448
00:31:29,452 --> 00:31:32,629
People still go out.
They spend an arm and a leg
for clothes that say, "Hey!

449
00:31:32,673 --> 00:31:35,937
<i>Look at me. I'm very powerful.</i><i>
I deserve respect."</i>

450
00:31:35,981 --> 00:31:38,766
