 of thinking.
- Of course.

451
00:31:38,809 --> 00:31:41,116
That's the way it is.

452
00:31:41,160 --> 00:31:45,686
That's all the time we have for
today's lecture on "Lifestyles
of the Rich and Foolish."

453
00:31:45,729 --> 00:31:49,646
I got things to do.

454
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:57,002
I'll get it.

455
00:32:01,180 --> 00:32:03,312
Good morning!
What can I do for you?

456
00:32:03,356 --> 00:32:05,227
