you would sell
a lot more cookies.

459
00:32:12,191 --> 00:32:15,411
I never say please
to the hired help.

460
00:32:15,455 --> 00:32:19,676
<i>I'm sorry. Alexandra's</i><i>
in one of her moods today.</i><i>
Is the lady of the house in?</i>

461
00:32:19,720 --> 00:32:22,288
You're speaking to her.

462
00:32:22,331 --> 00:32:27,423
