 a bit of an attitude problem.</i>
- Almost as bad as your girl.

465
00:32:38,043 --> 00:32:40,001
- Well, I never!
- I'm not surprised.

466
00:32:40,045 --> 00:32:44,005
<i>I'm also not interested</i><i>
in anything you're selling.</i><i>
Good day.</i>

467
00:32:53,275 --> 00:32:55,451
