my brief moment of peace.

468
00:32:55,495 --> 00:32:58,454
Relax, Oso, I'm giving you
the night off.

469
00:32:59,934 --> 00:33:02,284
- What are you making?
- Pancakes.

470
00:33:02,328 --> 00:33:05,287
- <i>Panqueques!</i>
