485
00:33:58,645 --> 00:34:03,171
<i>[ Miguel ] What are you doing?</i>Surrendering to our
late-night cravings.

486
00:34:03,215 --> 00:34:06,609
"Pancaca." <i>Panqueques con--</i>
[ Spanish ]

487
00:34:06,653 --> 00:34:09,743
No! <i>Sí!</i>And there are two left.
You can have 'em.

488
00:34:09,786 --> 00:34:14,052
I'm gonna go to sleep.
I cooked, you clean.

489
00:34:16,706 --> 00:34:20,058
Oh, man, I love these!

490
00:34:20,101 --> 00:34:25,193
When your sister isn't
being possessed by Satan,
she can be pretty nice.

491
00:34:25,237 --> 00:34:27,500
Catalina's not had
an easy life.

492
00:34:27,543 --> 00:34:31,852
<i>We lost our parents when we were</i><i>
very young. I came to California</i><i>
to live with an uncle.</i>

493
00:34:31,895 --> 00:34:35,116
