I can understand why.

495
00:34:37,162 --> 00:34:42,384
She wasn't like that then.
At least not at first.

496
00:34:42,428 --> 00:34:45,779
It's just that every time
she got close to one family,

497
00:34:45,822 --> 00:34:47,868
