It was nice meeting you,
"Carolina."

557
00:40:17,545 --> 00:40:20,069
Hell no!

558
00:40:20,113 --> 00:40:22,507
Listen to me, sweetheart.

559
00:40:22,550 --> 00:40:25,466
The Colombia-coffee-bean-pickin'
spokesperson look...

560
00:40:25,510 --> 00:40:29,427
is cute in a Latino
