663
00:47:14,396 --> 00:47:17,182
- Catalina--
- Don't worry, Oso.
 I'll teach you.

664
00:47:17,225 --> 00:47:18,966
To be honest--

665
00:47:19,010 --> 00:47:24,363
This is no time to be honest.
This is our evening of lies.
Come on.

666
00:49:12,558 --> 00:49:14,821
