before I could stop it.

669
00:49:23,873 --> 00:49:26,876
You know, Cat,
when you want to--

670
00:49:26,920 --> 00:49:29,879
You too, Oso.

671
00:49:29,923 --> 00:49:32,273
Let's go.

672
00:49:42,805 --> 00:49:46,157
Uh-uh. Allow me.
I will get the door.

673
00:49:51,336 --> 00:49:54,904
.Thanks, Cat.
