704
00:52:20,093 --> 00:52:22,487
This is... your holidays.

705
00:52:22,530 --> 00:52:25,925
So, how shall I say this?

706
00:52:25,968 --> 00:52:29,581
You are
citizenship-challenged.

707
00:52:29,624 --> 00:52:33,454
Donald, there's some things
