00:53:18,978 --> 00:53:21,154
We're from the
Department of Immigration.

719
00:53:21,198 --> 00:53:24,810
I swear to you.
 I did nothing to the gravy!

720
00:53:24,853 --> 00:53:26,812
I beg your pardon?

721
00:53:26,855 --> 00:53:31,643
For this, I place
