735
00:54:26,393 --> 00:54:29,266
- Mr. Chandler--
- She is a witch!
 Take her. She's yours!

736
00:54:31,137 --> 00:54:34,749
Thanks for coming by.

737
00:54:34,793 --> 00:54:37,056
I'll go pack my suitcases. <i>[ Man ]</i><i>
Mrs. Chandler.</i>

738
00:54:37,099 --> 00:54:40,494
We're not here to judge
whether or not
you're happily married.

739
00:54:40,538 --> 00:54:45,673
We're here to verify that
you're actually living together
as man and wife.

740
00:54:45,717 --> 00:54:49,286
Which apparently you are.

741
00:54:50,330 --> 00:54:52,550
<i>[ Donald ]</i><i>
I'm sorry.</i>

742
00:54:52,593 --> 00:54:54,813
I didn't mean
what I just said.
It's just my ties!

743
00:54:54,856 --> 00:54:58,338
I know.
I'm sorry too.

744
00:54:58,382 --> 00:55:01,210
I'll talk to you
when I get home.I'll be here.

745
00:55:02,908 --> 00:55:05,302
Mr. Chandler,
we'd like to ask you
a few questions.

746
00:55:05,345 --> 00:55:09,828
I'm sorry, but I have
to get to work. I'm late,
and I need some new ties.

747
00:55:12,613 --> 00:55:16,356
I'm sorry about Oso--
I mean, Donald.

748
00:55:16,400 --> 00:55:18,489
You don't need to apologize.

749
00:55:18,532 --> 00:55:24,364
Apparently you two share a very
passionate relationship.
I envy you.

750
00:55:32,720 --> 00:55:36,768
You're up late tonight.I'm trying to put together
Domi's gift.

751
00:55:36,811 --> 00:55:40,946
Mmm. This family has been
a good influence on you.

752
00:55:40,989 --> 00:55:44,123
I think maybe you
are beginning to find
your soul again.

753
00:55:44,166 --> 00:55:47,561
Blame it on the holidays.Would you like
an eggnog?

754
00:55:47,605 --> 00:55:50,390
No. I hate eggnog.Me too.

755
00:55:50,434 --> 00:55:54,307
But it's the holidays!

756
00:56:00,705 --> 00:56:04,186
Oso, there is something
I must tell you.

757
00:56:05,623 --> 00:56:07,799
- So tell me.
- I have wronged you.

758
00:56:07,842 --> 00:56:10,410
Anything in particular
or just in general?

759
00:56:10,454 --> 00:56:14,849
A few weeks ago when
the immigration people
came here,

760
00:56:14,893 --> 00:56:17,417
I thought you had sent them
to take me away.

761
00:56:17,461 --> 00:56:20,202
I placed a curse on you.

762
00:56:20,246 --> 00:56:22,596
Given the situation,
I don't blame you.

763
00:56:22,640 --> 00:56:27,427
It was a curse on you
