your greatest fear.

764
00:56:27,471 --> 00:56:32,693
<i>It's only recently</i><i>
I discovered what</i><i>
you fear the most.</i>

765
00:56:32,737 --> 00:56:34,652
You fear love.

766
00:56:34,695 --> 00:56:39,439
<i>It is why you have tried</i><i>
to bury yourself</i><i>
in all of this comfort.</i>

767
00:56:39,483 --> 00:56:43,530
