from feeling the things
you cannot control.

768
00:56:43,574 --> 00:56:47,839
You know something, Ansiana,
you would make
a hell of a fortune teller.

769
00:56:47,882 --> 00:56:50,885
It's a gift I have.

770
00:56:50,929 --> 00:56:54,628
I hate to burst your bubble,
but I don't believe in magic.

771
00:56:54,672 --> 00:56:58,415
While we're at it,
I don't believe that true love
exists in the real world.

772
00:56:58,458 --> 00:57:02,549
People who have lost
their souls
believe in very little.

773
00:57:02,593 --> 00:57:06,118
<i>There is something else</i><i>
I have to tell you.</i>

774
00:57:09,164 --> 00:57:12,994
<i>Something I have told</i><i>
to no one else.</i>

775
00:57:13,038 --> 00:57:16,084
- What is that?
