if I was related to them.

782
00:57:34,668 --> 00:57:39,717
- Why are you telling me this?
- I have lived with this secret
 for many years now.

783
00:57:39,760 --> 00:57:44,243
Sometimes it is good
to trust another with
the secrets of your heart.

784
00:57:44,286 --> 00:57:46,419
- And you trust me?
- [ Giggling ]

785
00:57:46,463 --> 00:57:51,859
In many ways,
you and Catalina
are so much alike.

786
00:57:51,903 --> 00:57:55,036
Good night.

787
00:57:55,080 --> 00:57:58,213
<i>Feliz Navidad.</i>

788
00:57:58,257 --> 00:57:59,911
Ah.

