800
00:58:42,910 --> 00:58:47,262
e@Sorry, Barbie,
but I've got commitments here.

801
00:58:47,306 --> 00:58:48,960
<i>Feliz Navidad.</i>

802
00:58:49,003 --> 00:58:51,136
<i>Feliz Navidad?</i>

803
00:59:04,758 --> 00:59:08,240
- Looking for something special?
- [ Gasps ]
 You startled me.

804
00:59:08,283 --> 00:59:10,677
So, Cat, are you being naughty
or nice?

805
00:59:10,721 --> 00:59:13,419
I haven't decided yet.

806
00:59:13,462 --> 00:59:17,684
[ Both Laughing ]

807
00:59:20,252 --> 00:59:23,690
I like your hat.

808
00:59:23,734 --> 00:59:28,695
So, little boy, what do
you want for Christmas?

809
00:59:28,739 --> 00:59:32,264
That, my dear,
is a very dangerous question
to ask a celibate.

810
00:59:32,307 --> 00:59:34,571
I know.

811
00:59:34,614 --> 00:59:39,358
- <i>[ Miguel ] Ho, ho, ho!</i>
- Great! Here comes
 Santa Claus.

812
00:59:40,838 --> 00:59:42,970
<i>Feliz Navidad, Oso.</i>

813
00:59:50,978 --> 00:59:52,893
Ho, ho, ho, my friend.

814
00:59:52,937 --> 00:59:55,330
wHumbug, amigo.

815
00:59:59,857 --> 01:00:04,513
<i>[ Crowd ]</i><i>
Five, four,</i><i>
three, two, one--</i>

816
01:00:04,557 --> 01:00:07,081
