01:00:13,131 --> 01:00:15,481
Happy New Year,
my almost-husband.

818
01:00:15,524 --> 01:00:18,005
Happy New Year,
my almost-wife.

819
01:00:18,049 --> 01:00:21,879
Happy New Year,
Catalina.Happy New Year!

